    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Architectural drawings that render the exteriors of structures and give the impression of relative position, size, or distance, as the structure would if viewed from a physical vantage point.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
